name: Mors Wild Boar & Singing Dog

-

Anjing menyanyi masuk halaman, mengejar babi hutan

Babi berlari takut kena liurnya
Anjing menghindar takut dikejar

Babi menggonggong. Anjing memekik

Ada kebingungan. Berdua lari berpencar
Meninggalkan kotoran berserakan,
jejak dua ketakutan.

-
Singing Dog in the yard try to chasing a Wild Boar

The Boar run afraid of getting Dog saliva
The Dog avoid being chased

Boar barking. Dog squealing

There is confusion. They're run apart
Leaving their shit scattered, traces of two fears.

-

From my old prose 'Boar & Dog' 2013.
